{"tid":895217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒指半日再瀉626點　騰訊再插4%","createTime":"2018-11-09T04:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T07:36:13.000Z","uid":147314,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b60eb8dd133e292cc65d92b892ea77e8000a7a32","tid":895217,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:19:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/1987845/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fstock%2Farticle%2F1987845%2F&d=DUsE54zVauZF%2B575uuwaAxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=b6f7f9df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/1987845/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恒指半日瀉626點失10天線 騰訊插4%</span></strong><br />\n今日 12:14<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/11/09/1987845_36e6921ec8b5eccdb106a8a85b13a6c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F1987845_36e6921ec8b5eccdb106a8a85b13a6c6.jpg&h=378ac935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國聯儲局議息後維持利率不變，會後聲明預計未來仍循序漸進式加息，美股一度倒跌，道指收市升10點，報26191點。港股昨日受制50天平均線之後，今早淡友發難，恒指遭質低逾六百點。<br />\n<br />\n恒指低開302點報25925，開市後跌幅隨即擴大，科技股、內銀AH股急跌拖累中港股市，恒指最多急插642點，低見25585，跌穿10天線(約25630)。恒指中午跌626點或2.4%，報25601。<br />\n<br />\n國企指數大跌284點或2.65%，報10419。<br />\n<br />\n大市半日成交498.54億元。<br />\n<br />\n50隻藍籌股全部向下，騰訊(00700)插近4%報282元，成交居首有41.9億元。<br />\n<br />\n成交第二大是建行(00939)，半日跌2.4%；工行(01398)挫近3%，招行(03968)插逾半成。市場憂慮內銀要加大向民企放貸，同時要降低貸款利率，對淨息差承受更大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n瑞聲(02018)季績差過預期，遭多家券商調低目標價，半日插4.7%報53.15元，為表現最差藍籌。"},{"pid":"1544ff4bf3572bb3acb2c9fd4709b73db1a7a91b","tid":895217,"uid":108236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"聽日上番300啦 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c2e3965e541855bdec07ec0ea88184ab9146b6","tid":895217,"uid":